info: Rating, 5 stars,  · May 2022,  · Stayed about a week
rating_comment: Communication with Tamzid was great from my very first inquiries about the room. He was flexible and understanding about my change in plans. He arranged a very well needed airport pickup. He provided extremely valuable information regarding the city, services and options for tourists short and long term. Great value for the money as well. I recommend this room.
